  "title": "SALES",
  "description": "<p><strong>Want to join our team?</strong></p><p>To cope with our business expansion, we are inviting candidate to join us!</p><ul><li>Retail Sales Associate by a health service provider and on job training provided.</li><li>Salary & sales commission are competitive</li><li>Career Development</li><li>5.5days work-week</li></ul><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Ensure merchandise and displays are consistently well presented.</li><li>Attend to walk in customers and demonstrate products, share health care knowledge according to their needs.</li><li>Perform daily housekeeping of the store to ensure cleanliness of the store to our customers.</li><li>To understand the products and the environment in which they are sold, to understand what customers are looking for and to present them in an appropriate way</li><li>To ensure that physical stock levels are in line with the stock held in the system.</li><li>Ensure shop cleanliness.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min O Level education</li><li>Fresh graduated/Non-experience are welcomed. Training will be provided</li><li>Sales and result-oriented</li><li>Able to liaise with Mandarin speaking customers.</li><li>Good customer service skill</li><li>Self-motivated and a great team player</li><li>Highly committed and willing to learn healthcare related knowledge</li><li>Kindness towards elderly</li></ul>",
